                  <handDesc>
                     <p>Written in a large and inelegant but fluent hand with frequent ligatures and under considerable cursive influence; at times a space is left between words. The length of the line can probably be established from lines 10-11 of the verso (approx. 30 letters). Pagination survives only on the verso; the internal evidence is slightly in favor of recto preceding verso.</p>
